t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e236094 ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2e236094\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">FTP SERVER\/DROPBOX\/ONEDRIVE\/GDRIVE EXCHANGE PROCEDURE<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"ob-is-breaking-bad ob-bb-inner elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-c73c346 elementor-reverse-mobile elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c73c346\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_bbad_use_it&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;,&quot;_ob_bbad_sssic_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_glider_is_slider&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-32aa7daa\" data-id=\"32aa7daa\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_bbad_is_stalker&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_teleporter_use&quot;:false,&quot;_ob_column_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_column_has_pseudo&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33ced188 ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"33ced188\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Quality work with Systematic approach<\/strong><\/p><p>With a systematic and step by step process, you can get most out of outsourcing your work to us and take your practice to next level. The better you understand and follow the process the more easily and convenient it gets for you to utilize our strength to obtain the maximum possible results. Take a look on the below &#8220;PROCESS STEPS&#8221; starting from left to right in chronologically to understand how exactly it works-<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-17d73c43 elementor-tabs-view-vertical elementor-tabs-alignment-stretch elementor-widget elementor-widget-tabs\" data-id=\"17d73c43\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"tabs.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tabs\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tabs-wrapper\" role=\"tablist\" >\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-3991\" class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-desktop-title\" aria-selected=\"true\" data-tab=\"1\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3991\" aria-expanded=\"false\">1. Scanning<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-3992\" class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-desktop-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"2\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3992\" aria-expanded=\"false\">2. Upload<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-3993\" class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-desktop-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"3\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3993\" aria-expanded=\"false\">3. Inform<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-3994\" class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-desktop-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"4\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3994\" aria-expanded=\"false\">4. Analysis<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-3995\" class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-desktop-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"5\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3995\" aria-expanded=\"false\">5. Queries<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-3996\" class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-desktop-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"6\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3996\" aria-expanded=\"false\">6. Accomplishment<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-3997\" class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-desktop-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"7\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3997\" aria-expanded=\"false\">7. Updates<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-title-3998\" class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-desktop-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"8\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3998\" aria-expanded=\"false\">8. Deliver<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tabs-content-wrapper\" role=\"tablist\" aria-orientation=\"vertical\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-mobile-title\" aria-selected=\"true\" data-tab=\"1\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"0\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3991\" aria-expanded=\"false\">1. Scanning<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-3991\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"1\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-3991\" tabindex=\"0\" hidden=\"false\"><p>At first you scan the documents (bank statements, invoices etc.) which you received from your end clients.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-mobile-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"2\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3992\" aria-expanded=\"false\">2. Upload<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-3992\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"2\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-3992\" tabindex=\"0\" hidden=\"hidden\"><ol><li>Second step is to upload the scanned copies of the documents to &#8220;shared Dropbox folder\/Common or shared Drive folder\/FTP Server&#8221; whichever applicable.<\/li><\/ol><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-mobile-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"3\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3993\" aria-expanded=\"false\">3. Inform<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-3993\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"3\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-3993\" tabindex=\"0\" hidden=\"hidden\"><p>After uploading the docs, inform us via email with a subject as &#8216;name of the company-nature&#8217; i.e. XYZ LTD &#8211; YE 2019. Please mention about the uploaded documents, deadline of the job, any other points to take care of, in the body of the email.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-mobile-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"4\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3994\" aria-expanded=\"false\">4. Analysis<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-3994\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"4\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-3994\" tabindex=\"0\" hidden=\"hidden\"><p>After we receive the documents in the Drobox\/Shared Drive, we then start analysis of the data to find out what else could be required to accomplish the job and how much time it can take.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-mobile-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"5\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3995\" aria-expanded=\"false\">5. Queries<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-3995\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"5\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-3995\" tabindex=\"0\" hidden=\"hidden\"><p>Once we analyze the data we send you the queries for missing information through email and wait to receive the replies for the same from you.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-mobile-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"6\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3996\" aria-expanded=\"false\">6. Accomplishment<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-3996\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"6\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-3996\" tabindex=\"0\" hidden=\"hidden\"><p>After receiving the replies on the queries- we complete the work and upload the job on the Dropbox\/Drive\/Server.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-mobile-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"7\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3997\" aria-expanded=\"false\">7. Updates<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-3997\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"7\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-3997\" tabindex=\"0\" hidden=\"hidden\"><p>In this step, you fetch the completed job from the Drive\/Dropbox\/Server to a last final check at your end before sending to your end clients and we do the final updates required if any.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-tab-title elementor-tab-mobile-title\" aria-selected=\"false\" data-tab=\"8\" role=\"tab\" tabindex=\"-1\" aria-controls=\"elementor-tab-content-3998\" aria-expanded=\"false\">8. Deliver<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"elementor-tab-content-3998\" class=\"elementor-tab-content elementor-clearfix\" data-tab=\"8\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"elementor-tab-title-3998\" tabindex=\"0\" hidden=\"hidden\"><p>After all the updates are done, we save the changes in the job on Dropbox\/Drive\/Server and confirm the same via email and now you can happily send the job to your end client.<\/p><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-665e18c3\" data-id=\"665e18c3\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_bbad_is_stalker&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_teleporter_use&quot;:false,&quot;_ob_column_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_column_has_pseudo&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-23840b9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"23840b9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_photomorph_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/mobile-flow-chat-watermarked.png\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/mobile-flow-chat-watermarked.png 1080w, https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/mobile-flow-chat-watermarked-253x300.png 253w, https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/mobile-flow-chat-watermarked-864x1024.png 864w, https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/mobile-flow-chat-watermarked-768x910.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7aaaaa3d ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7aaaaa3d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Method 2<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-53c0b3d ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"53c0b3d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">EMAIL EXCHANGE METHOD<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7db18857 ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7db18857\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In this method, the exchange of data and information happens through the email channel only. When you upload a job, you simply compose an email, highlights the name of the job as subject i.e. xyz ltd-YE 30.12.2020 or abc ltd-VAT QE 30.08.2020 etc. and then you mention all the relevant points in the email itself. You can describe if there is anything in the job which needs special attention or treatment, you can mention the deadline and the desired budget of the job.<br \/>Generally, this method most suited when the data size is not too large otherwise it always go along with the use of any cloud storage services like Dropbox, One drive etc. wherein you can upload the job on a shared folder on preferred cloud app and intimate us through email channel.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6cc49951 ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6cc49951\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Method 3<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-61b5cc5b ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"61b5cc5b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Remote desktop\/VPN<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7f8718b4 ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7f8718b4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>In this method, you provide us the access to one your in-house computer through your company\u2019s VPN or through any third party remote application like Team Viewer, Anydesk, Log me In etc.<br \/>The accountants at our end use the provided credentials to access to the remote PC and performs his\/her assigned tasks.<br \/>This method is equally secured just as the above two methods are but yes, the efficiency depends upon the internet speed at both ends in all of the methods described till now.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-486ae7e2 ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"486ae7e2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Method 4<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-359f4ffe ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"359f4ffe\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Online Software Procedure<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6ee98ccb ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6ee98ccb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>If you use any kind of online software for bookkeeping, final accounts, payroll and tax i.e. Quickbooks and Xero then this is the procedure you would want to follow.<br \/>You either provide your access credentials to us to login to your accounting software or you create\/buy a separate access for us and then our team access the software online to perform the routine work.<br \/>This method is highly popular and efficient since it is always easy to work in online mode now a days.<br \/>The email channel in this method is just used to inform the other side about the development in the job or if there are any queries then they would exchange through the emails only.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-283c7b26 ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"283c7b26\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Method 5<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6e61458d ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6e61458d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Desktop\/Offline software<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-308d2022 ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"308d2022\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>If you use any offline\/desktop accounting software like VT+, Sage50 etc. and if you have more than one users on your license then you can provide the license details and login credentials to us and we can simply download the software at our end to perform all the desired accounting activities for you.<br \/>The best part of this method is that it is not dependent on the internet to perform the core activities however one would always need the internet to queries, back up of the completed files and to share the path of job if the completed jobs are stored on cloud storage like Dropbox , One drive etc.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6daf7664 ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"6daf7664\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Method 6<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7c36ead8 ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7c36ead8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Using Team Collaboration apps and software<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-190cd33c ob-harakiri-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"190cd33c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_ob_harakiri_writing_mode&quot;:&quot;inherit&quot;,&quot;_ob_perspektive_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_shadough_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_allow_hoveranimator&quot;:&quot;no&quot;,&quot;_ob_widget_stalker_use&quot;:&quot;no&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>There is one more way to exchange the information\/data, share ideas, suggestions and to collaborate in real time with the use of Skype, Slack, Microsoft Teams, Whatsapp Group etc. and many more other unexplored apps.<br \/>You can create communication channels or group on the above apps and collaborate with us in real time. These apps give you an extra edge since they allow to have video conferences, you can add other supportive applications to these main apps to perform various other tasks.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Our Methodologies Method 1 FTP SERVER\/DROPBOX\/ONEDRIVE\/GDRIVE EXCHANGE PROCEDURE Quality work with Systematic approach With a systematic and step by step process, you can get most out of outsourcing your work to us and take your practice to next level. The better you understand and follow the process the more easily and convenient it gets for [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":6,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/585"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=585"}],"version-history":[{"count":13,"href":"https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/585\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":936,"href":"https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/585\/revisions\/936"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/6"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/lekhawekha.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=585"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}